name: W_SERIES_003: The Cannibalized
description: A vast hulk of derelict spaceship hangs over the city. Itâ€™s like the bloated corpse of some great dead whale, rotting away as it is slowly ransacked for parts. This edition of 20 is issued just for the early adopters of the project who joined our discord in the first draft as a special thank you
